    "description": "<i><strong>''Executioner! Hunt down the traitor who dares to proclaim himself the king and bring peace to the Empire!''</strong></i><br><br>Our Little Chase is a strategy-action game where you start with only yourself and gradually build up your army to face the traitor.<br><br>This game combines real-time battles with roguelike campaign map as you move from point to point toward your goal. Inspired by 'Mount and Blade' and 'Total War' series.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Procedurally generated map to ensure replay value.<br></li><li> Unique handcrafted maps<br></li><li> Control your army directly to fight for you or join in the fight yourself.<br></li><li> Or sneak away from your enemies. Remember your target is the traitor.<br></li><li> Permanent death, so think twice before joining the combat.<br></li><li> Fully customizable arsenal for your character and your troops.<br></li><li> Manage your inventory, make sure you have enough supplies for your troops.<br></li><li> Interrogate the villager, find out where that traitor has gone to.<br></li><li> Every choice has a consequence.<br></li><li> Multiple ending.</li></ul>",
